<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="/favicon.ico" type="image/x-icon" />
    <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.ico" type="image/x-icon" />
    <link href="css/style.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, maximum-scale=1">
    <title>concert playlists | flipthewaffle.com | easily digestable concert playlists</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Flipthewaffle.com is your source for Spotify concert playlists." />
    <meta name="keywords" content="concert, playlist, spotify, spotify playlist" />
  </head>
  <body class="home">
  	<script>
      (function(i,s,o,g,r,a,m){i['GoogleAnalyticsObject']=r;i[r]=i[r]||function(){
      (i[r].q=i[r].q||[]).push(arguments)},i[r].l=1*new Date();a=s.createElement(o),
      m=s.getElementsByTagName(o)[0];a.async=1;a.src=g;m.parentNode.insertBefore(a,m)
      })(window,document,'script','//www.google-analytics.com/analytics.js','ga');

      ga('create', 'UA-63501311-1', 'auto');
      ga('send', 'pageview');

    </script>
    <div class="intro">
      <div class="container">
        <img src="/images/logo-green.png">
        <p>
          Do you like music? Do you like concerts? Maybe you like playlists to get preppin' ready for your concert blowout experience.  If you do then this site is most definitely for you.
        </p>
        <p>
          These playlists are 100% artisinally crafted for your auditory pleasure.  Flip The Waffle playlists are easily digestable concert playlists.  What does "easily digestable concert playlist" mean?  It means that these playlists are easy to follow on Spotify.  These playlists will rock your socks off.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="playlist-container">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <h2 class="centered">
            some of our playlists...
          </h3>
        </div>
        {% for row in playlists|batch(3) %}
        	<div class="row">
	        	{% for slug,playlist in row %}
	        		<div class="grid-4 playlist-preview">
		            	<a href="{{ path('playlist', {slug: slug}) }}">
			              <div class="overlay-container">
			                <img alt="{{ playlist.name }}" src="{{ playlist.image }}">
			                <div class="overlay">
			                  <span class="title">{{ playlist.name }}</span>
			                </div>
			              </div>
		            	</a>
		          	</div>
	        	{% endfor %}
        	</div>
        {% endfor %}
        
      </div>
    </div>
    <footer class="footer">
      <span class="centered">Created by <a href=
      "http://easander.com/">chicohernando</a>. Designed by
      <a href="http://www.github.com/niederer">niederer</a>.</span>
    </footer>
    <script src="//code.jquery.com/jquery-1.11.0.min.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>